VPC Peering
=============
1.Requester of VPC peering connection
2.Acceptor of VPC peering connection.

>The owner of the acceptor VPC peering connection must accept the request for the peering connection to be active.
>There should be no CIDR overlap between acceptor and requestor VPC
>The security group of both the VPC should allow to flow to/from acceptor/requestor VPC
>A vpc cannot be used as a transit point.

VPC Peering lifecycle
======================

init---->Pending--->provisioning------>active
  |        |           |                  |
  Failed   Expired     rejected           |
